This prof is not clear in her instruction and can be confusing at times. The tests are long and difficult. The midterm was altered mid-exam and in the final exam, she asked a question involving material we had not covered or been exposed to prior to the exam. Despite these criticisms, she could be helpful to her students and was kind at times.
